<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Verify Your UniNav Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333; /* --text-color-dark approximation */
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f0f8ff; /* --bg-main */
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
      color: #f0f8ff; /* --text-color-light-two */
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ccebff; /* Lighter shade derived from --border-color */
      border-top: none;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280; /* --muted-foreground approximation */
    }
    .verification-code {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #e6f2ff; /* Lighter shade of --bg-main */
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
    }
    .button {
      display: block;
      background-color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
      color: #f0f8ff !important; /* --text-color-light-two, !important */
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      width: 200px;
      border: none;
    }
     .button:hover {
       background-color: #002a50; /* Slightly darker shade of --bg-dark for hover */
    }
    .expiry {
      color: #ef4444; /* --destructive approximation */
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
     a { /* Standard link color */
        color: #003666; /* --bg-dark */
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for registering with UniNav. To complete your registration and gain full access to our academic resource platform, please verify your email address.</p>

    <p>You can verify your email by clicking the button below:</p>

    <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button" style="color: #f0f8ff !important;">Verify Email Address</a>

    <p>Alternatively, you can enter this verification code on the verification page:</p>

    <div class="verification-code"><%= verificationCode %></div>

    <p class="expiry">This verification link and code will expire in 15 minutes.</p>

    <p>If you didn't create an account with UniNav, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Welcome to our academic community!</p>
    <p>The UniNav Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> UniNav. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to verify your account. If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@uninav.com" style="color: #003666;">support@uninav.com</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
